com.esri.mo2.ui.dnd
Class DndManager

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.ui.dnd.DndManager
public final class DndManager
extends Object

Defines a drag and drop generic framework associating with a component. A component can register itself either as drag source or drop target, or both to this DndManager. The DndManager maintains a list of DndHandler(s). When a drag event happens, dependent upon the type of transferable data flavor to decide which the DndHandler is called.


The component only can register one DndHandler as drag source; however it can has many DndHandlers to handle the different data flavor dropping.
